import React from "react"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; // components import background from '../../assets/img/1634671651-3856.webp' import Navbar from "components/Navbars/AuthNavbar.js"; import Footer from "components/Footers/Footer.js"; export default function Power() { return ( <>

Welcome to Power Circle

Power circle of EIES expands the public awareness of the many faces of power engineering and how they affect ongoing increasingly developing energy demand. Our circle mainly focuses on the decaying energy grid infrastructure and the need for more innovative ways of power generation within the country.

Our Vision

To gather students interested in power engineering and guide them to perform best in the industry by creating opportunities and encouraging them to seek novel trends.

Our Mission

To be the mediating platform between power industry and university, which will create opportunities for students to become experts in power engineering.

Power Circle - Committee Members 2021/2022

Nirmani Rathnayaka

President

Nisal Dulanjana

Secretary

Gihan Kavinda

Editor

Madhura Pabudanan

Committee Member

Sampavi Sivakumaran

Committee Member
